						<summary>

						<p>This is probably an inscription of Ariñjaya like Nos. 11 and 12 above. This records a gift of 12(1/2) <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for a perpetual lamp in the temple on behalf of Āchchaṉ Baladēvan (perhaps deceased) by members of the regiment <hi rend="bold">Parāntaka-teriñja-Kaikkōḷar.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
